cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CC

This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category as it deals with synaptic plasticity and neural dynamics. It could also be classified under the Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it proposes a new weight update formula for machine learning models. The paper also discusses the potential application of the proposed rule in studying systems and control (cs.SY) and computational complexity (cs.CC), which are additional possible categories.
